[{"id":"552ff3fc8d8902de2eb6313bc980d055","from":"Mark L. Epstein","from_email":"izmo@mindspring.com","to":"jeeproject@yahoo.com","to_list":[{"name":"jeeproject@yahoo.com","email":"jeeproject@yahoo.com"}],"cc_list":[],"subject":"FW","date":"2007-09-14T23:17:45.000Z","formatted_date":"Sep 14, 2007","formatted_time":"11:17 PM","body":"\n\nizmo@mindspring.com\nEarthLink Revolves Around You.\n\n\n----- Original Message ----- \nFrom: \nTo: izmo@mindspring.com\nSent: 9/14/2007 10:01:22 AM \nSubject: GET A LOAD OF DIS! MISSED MY CALLING!\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\nFederal Prison Consultants, LLC is an organization that takes great pride in helping people. To learn what Criminal Defense Attorneys , Experts, and Clients, alike, think about Federal Prison Consultants , LLC, please click on our Testimonials Page . These documents are completely original and only private information has been removed to protect the identity of our clients. You will see actual judicial orders , correspondence from Prison Administrators , and various email. \n\nBeing aware of critical, up to date, information is one of the skills that make Federal Prison Consultants, LLC, proven and documented specialists in Federal Prison & State Prison reduction strategies, rehabilitation programming, prisoner rights and advocacy . Please review the Statistics Page to see actual graphs in the Compendium of Federal Justice Statistics . \n\n\n\nRetainer Policy \n\n\nManaging Director's Premium$5,000.00\nState Prison Review & Placement Package $4,000.00\n500 Hour RDAP Program Strategic Consulting $4,500.00\nRDAP Psychological Assessment Report* $2,500.00\nLegislative Action Plan*$2,500.00\nTravel Day Rate Plus Expenses$2,500.00\nExpert Witness Day Rate Plus Expenses$4,000.00\nJudicial Recommendations*$2,500.00\nPublic Works & Community Service Projects$4,000.00\nPlea Agreement Review & Recommendations $4,000.00\nPre-Sentence Report Review & Recommendations $4,000.00\nDesignation or Redesignation Issues $3,500.00 \nInstitutional Transfer $4,000.00\nCCC-Half-Way House $4,000.00\nHome Confinement Request $4,000.00\nCompassionate Release Request $4,000.00\nMothers & Infants Together (MINT) Program Request $4,000.00\nTreaty Transfer Request $4,500.00\nCommutation of Sentence Petition $4,000.00\nPardon Request $4,000.00\nParole, Probation, or Supervised Release Issues $4,000.00\nFurlough Request $4,000.00\nAdministrative Remedy Program$4,000.00\nPSF - Public Safety Factors $4,000.00\nManagement Variables$4,000.00\nGood Time Credit Issues $4,000.00\nOur Rate Per Hour$400.00\n\n\n\n\nConsulting Services: \n\nManaging Director's Premium\nIf you would like the Managing Director to service your consulting package exclusively, FPC will add a premium to the quoted fees.\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\nEmail and AIM finally together. You've gotta check out free AOL Mail!","body_html":"<HTML><HEAD>\n<META content=\"MSHTML 6.00.2900.3157\" name=GENERATOR></HEAD>\n<BODY>\n<DIV>\n<DIV>&nbsp;</DIV>\n<DIV>&nbsp;</DIV>\n<DIV>\n<DIV><A href=\"mailto:izmo@mindspring.com\">izmo@mindspring.com</A></DIV>\n<DIV>EarthLink Revolves Around You.</DIV>\n<DIV>&nbsp;</DIV></DIV></DIV>\n<DIV>&nbsp;</DIV>\n<BLOCKQUOTE style=\"PADDING-RIGHT: 0px; PADDING-LEFT: 5px; MARGIN-LEFT: 5px; BORDER-LEFT: #000000 2px solid\">\n<DIV style=\"FONT: 10pt Arial\">----- Original Message ----- </DIV>\n<DIV style=\"BACKGROUND: #e4e4e4; FONT: 10pt arial; font-color: black\"><B>From:</B> <A title=tommygendru@aol.com href=\"mailto:tommygendru@aol.com\"></A></DIV>\n<DIV style=\"FONT: 10pt arial\"><B>To: </B><A title=izmo@mindspring.com href=\"mailto:izmo@mindspring.com\">izmo@mindspring.com</A></DIV>\n<DIV style=\"FONT: 10pt arial\"><B>Sent:</B> 9/14/2007 10:01:22 AM </DIV>\n<DIV style=\"FONT: 10pt arial\"><B>Subject:</B> GET A LOAD OF DIS! MISSED MY CALLING!</DIV>\n<DIV><BR></DIV><FONT size=2>\n<TABLE cellSpacing=0 cellPadding=0 width=707 align=center border=0>\n<TBODY>\n<TR>\n<TD vAlign=top align=left><IMG height=159 src=\"http://www.federalprisonconsultants